videos.headline: Miami picks off Nebraska in overtime win
videos.description: Cornelius Elder intercepted Tommie Armstrong Jr. in the end zone on the first play of overtime, that set up Miami's game-winning FG. Nebraska had forced the extra session by scoring 23 straight points in the fourth quarter.
